    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm confused. A second ago you were saying there should be \"some room to opt out\" and that respecting faith ensures diversity, but now you're saying exceptions \"should not be allowed\" because they jeopardize the rule of law. Which is it? Are you saying that religious freedom is actually a threat to equality?",
